## Request Context

All middleware has access to:
```json
{
  "params": {}, "query": {}, "body": {},
  "headers": {}, "method": "GET", "path": "/api/users"
}
```

JQ accesses context via `$context` (e.g., `$context.flags`, `$context.conditions`, `$context.rate_limit`).
Lua accesses context via the `context` table. Handlebars via `{{context.env}}`.
